data.description: Check out this cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in Cave City sitting on 4 acres! This home has many great features, including an open floor plan, a large porch with fans to keep you cool in the summer, and a 25x30 shop. The shop has heat, electric, plumbing, and a full bathroom as well! New propane gas lines, a new hot water heater, and new plumbing in the shop all in 2023. Home and shop both have propane heat as a backup source for those cold winters! Don’t forget the fully fenced land, great for a hobby farm or any other dream you can think of! Wildlife is also abundant on this property! Country living with a short drive to town! Don’t miss out on this one!
